{"tid":335950,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「請教」假如明報接受投訴，因仇思達高唱支那二字，拒絕售賣屹屹屹","createTime":"2017-07-26T04:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T22:44:16.000Z","uid":30807,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"989aa3533034e383e0b2bfeda46c0a2bb2043ee4","tid":335950,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:28:50.000Z","msg":"「請教」假如明報接受投訴，因仇思達高唱支那二字，拒絕售賣屹屹屹，熱血時報會點報？<br />\n<br />\n會唔會報明報染紅？因為作者係書展唱歌有支那(其實是芝麻)二字就被明報打壓？<br />\n<br />\n但係根據往例，佢地係唔會報導埋異教者既名，所以標題可能好似下面咁：<br />\n「明報染紅又一實證！明報因某新作某作者高歌時加入支那二字，不再售賣該作者之作品」<br />\n<br />\n定係完全唔理，當冇事發生？<br />\n<br />\n熱血時報有個每週赤化新聞，會唔會將呢單野加入去？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家可以以熱狗往常慣例推測下！<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f7f052b2108dc455e4ae2027b66beb6c428eb7","tid":335950,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打有第三個可能性？"},{"pid":"bb458eefa73979f878c80494112bd1b593c87ae5","tid":335950,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:17:38.000Z","msg":"冇討論價值？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622c30eef6d70fc8a60c734c5e3f875c89eef5ef","tid":335950,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:25:39.000Z","msg":"熱狗嘅指控本身就存在矛盾，此post 已完"},{"pid":"2446719190c523d291b5e60e7d982846a5bcaa5e","tid":335950,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:33:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熱狗嘅指控本身就存在矛盾，此post 已完</blockquote><br />\nD人又唔係熱狗，只係睇唔過眼既路人姐~"},{"pid":"7876e459804c92722e7a7d35a9acacaab6b6ab16","tid":335950,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:33:25.000Z","msg":"(好似係)"},{"pid":"d9dbd1d8b6dd28e7a9b5103786ec63ff1eff3153","tid":335950,"uid":60341,"like":2,"di